article_title: Google, Oracle, Red Hat experts to help fix Obamacare website

article_metadata.description: WASHINGTON- Experts from top technology and Internet companies including Google Inc, Oracle Corp and Red Hat Inc have joined the Obama administrations effort to fix its troubled HealthCare.gov website, a U.S. official said on Thursday.
